  m_text: "\"Year 2036.\n\nAfter many years of excessive industrial exploitation,
    emissions and household waste have destroyed the living environment, turning
    many areas into heavily polluted zones no longer safe for humans. The air is
    thick with pollution, visibility is severely limited, and toxic substances permeate
    the surroundings.\n\nThe main character is stranded outside a safe shelter. With
    only a single gas mask in their possession, the player\u2019s sole objective
    is to find a way back to the safe shelter before their health is completely depleted.\""
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 7143f22c2ab0b2b4391efc7468622a24, type: 2}
