  m_text: '"Press Q to switch between two states:


    State 1: Wearing the gas
    mask

    Health drains more slowly

    Vision is limited, only a small area
    around the character is visible


    State 2: Not wearing the gas mask

    Health
    drains faster

    Vision is wider, allowing the player to clearly see the surrounding
    area"'
